	over 2\,500 attendees and 35\\+ talented vendors from our community. We're
	 so excited to welcome you to our winter edition!⏰ When: Sunday\, Feb 15 |
	 11-5 PM\\* Where: THE 101 \\(101 S Jackson St\, Seattle\, WA 98 104\\)Wha
	t to expect:\\* 35\\+ curated artists and makers\\* Live DJ bringing the g
	ood vibes\\* Henna designs\\* Free\, family-friendly\, and accessible \\(m
	a sks highly encouraged\\)\\* Kids crafts and activities\\* More surprises
	 TBA soon!Follow us on IG: @souk.seattleSee you soon \\* لنجتمع قريباً\n\n
	Neighborhoods: Pioneer Square\n\nEvent Types: Arts\,Community\,Festivals/F
	airs \,Music\n\nAudience: All\,Children\,Family\,Pets\,Senior\,Special Nee
	ds \,Teen\n\nSponsoring Organization: SOUK Seattle\n\nContact: souk.seattl
	e@gmail.com\n\nContact Email: souk.seattle@gmail.com\n\nPre-Register: Yes\
	n\nCost: Free\n\nLink: https://trybe.fm/event/souk-seattle-pop-up-market-o
	r-winter-edition/\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Arts & Culture
