UID:ME_0-SrWOdndJ3Ing9xtU
SUMMARY:PACIFIC PLACE TO HOST THREE-DAY ART MARKET
DTSTAMP:20260214T003622Z
DTSTART:20260228T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:Pacific Place\, a premier five-story shopping center in downtow
	n Seattle \\(www.pacificplaceseattle.com\\)\, invites the community to att
	end the “Pacific Place Art Market\,” taking place in partnership with Down
	town Seattle Art Walk\, on Friday\, February 27th \\(4 p.m. to 8 p.m.\\)\;
	 Saturday\, February 28th \\(1 p.m. to 5 p.m.\\)\; and Sunday\, March 1st 
	\\(noon to 4 p.m.\\). Attendees can immerse themselves in local art and cu
	lture while enjoying festive music and a gallery exhibit. Guests are encou
	raged to explore the center’s on-site art galleries\, shops and restaurant
	s during the event. The market will be held on Level 4 and is free of char
	ge and open to the public\; no pre-registration is required. To learn more
	\, click here or visit https://pacificplaceseattle.com/events.\n\nWHEN: Th
	ree-Day Art Market:\n\nFriday\, February 27th: 4 p.m. – 8 p.m.\n\nSaturday
	\, February 28th: 1 p.m. – 5 p.m.\n\nSunday\, March 1st: Noon – 4 p.m.\n\n
	From SEAtoday - Arts & Culture
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/pacific-place-to-host-thr
	ee-day-art-market/18117358/2026-02-27T00
LOCATION:PACIFIC PLACE\, 600 Pine Street\, Seattle\, WA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT4H
END:VEVENT
